title: Hour 1: I'm F***in Fantastic
description:
On this episode, Jay Glazer joins Dan and the Shipping Container to absolutely destroy our censors (there are a lot of F words in this podcast) and break down the major NFL stories including the Bills still being favorites, Daniel Snyder, and Russell Wilson's struggles. Plus, Jay tells the story about the healing experience he had with a Monk in Thailand. You can hear more about Jay Glazer's mental health journey on the Unbreakable podcast.
